    <item>
      <title>Version 8.0.2</title>
      <description><![CDATA[• Fix Zoom sharing issue where the zoomed-in window was not appearing on screen recording apps.<br />
• Return focus to the previous app after annotation is done.<br />
• Draw squares and circles by holding the Shift key.<br />
• New key shortcut to change Zoom modes.<br />
• UI fixes, code and memory improvements.<br />
]]></description>
